# HG changeset patch
# User Brian Grinstead <bgrinstead@mozilla.com>
# Parent  cebfaafafc89d07e3723cf86995330e6d3367a43
Bug 1392367 - Replace <label> with <firefox-label>

Script to build this patch:
perl -pi -e 's!<label!<firefox-label!g' browser/components/preferences/in-content-new/*.xul &&
perl -pi -e 's!</label!</firefox-label!g' browser/components/preferences/in-content-new/*.xul &&
perl -pi -e 's!^label!firefox-label!g' browser/themes/shared/incontentprefs/preferences.inc.css &&
perl -pi -e 's! label! firefox-label!g' browser/themes/shared/incontentprefs/preferences.inc.css


